title: Community: Some Channels are not loading in the Status Internal community
body:
Version: 0.13.1
OS: Windows 10

***
Preconditions: Install 0.13.1

<ins>Steps to reproduce:</ins>

1. Navigate to the internal Status community 

2.  Click on a channel that has an unread messages 

<ins>What currently incorrectly happens:</ins>

3. The channel messages aren't loading


https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/124154641/5cab019e-5b89-4a61-8ee2-73a03fc48da4



<ins>What is supposed to happen:</ins>

3. The messages in the channel should load
